snippet.title: Bow Bots - Official Silos Multiplayer Map Reveal Trailer | Upload VR Showcase
snippet.description: Bow Bots is a VR multiplayer bow and arrow shooter developed by Siege Industries. Take a look at the latest trailer to see a new multiplayer map be showcased called Silos. The Silos map is available now for Bow Bots on Meta Quest with a release on SteamVR and PICO coming soon.
